splay:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua (29/7), Barcelona tr\u1ea3i qua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u1edbi Tottenham t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup tr\u00ean n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1ef9. H\u1ecd d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh 2-0 song b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a v\u00e0o n\u1eeda sau hi\u1ec7p 2. Sau c\u00f9ng, Barca v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-3 tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng Denis Suarez v\u00e0 Andre Gomes d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Barca b\u1ecb lu m\u1edd. H\u1ecd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t r\u1eddi s\u00e2n c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 22 v\u00e0 26 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Carles Perez v\u00e0 Ricard Puig.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Denis Suarez v\u00e0 Andre Gomes d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1edbm tr\u1edf t\u1ea1i TBN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Denis Suarez v\u00e0 Andre Gomes d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1edbm tr\u1edf t\u1ea1i TBN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Suarez-va-Gomes.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Denis Suarez v\u00e0 Andre Gomes d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a International Champions Cup c\u1ee7a Suarez v\u00e0 Gomes.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ng\u1eafn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Barca x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Suarez v\u00e0 Gomes \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb Los Angeles, M\u1ef9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u201cDenis Suarez v\u00e0 Andre Gomes s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Barcelona t\u1eeb Los Angeles v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m Ciutat Esportiva \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 chi ti\u1ebft m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d,<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt tr\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p khi c\u1ea3 Suarez v\u00e0 Gomes \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb Barca thanh l\u00fd trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/andre-gomes-muon-toi-tottenham-172-191411.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/6/andre-gomes-muon-toi-tottenham.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/andre-gomes-muon-toi-tottenham-172-191411.html\">Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f9ng Harry Kane t\u1ea1i Premier League</span><br>\r\n<span>Ng\u00f4i sao b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng t\u1ea1i Barca, Andre Gomes d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp Tottenham, theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay c\u1ea3 khi Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 Paulinho l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t r\u1eddi Barca h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng (l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Vissel Kobe v\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande), Suarez v\u00e0 Gomes v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Blaugrana nh\u1eafm b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Miralem Pjanic (Juventus) v\u00e0 Frenkie de Jong (Ajax).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Barca \u0111\u00e3 mua g\u1ea5p Arthur t\u1eeb Gremio v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro d\u00f9 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2019 m\u1edbi mang anh v\u1ec1. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, nh\u1eefng Clement Lenglet v\u00e0 Malcom t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Sevilla v\u00e0 Bordeaux c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nang-gia-hoi-mua-mina-len-35-trieu-bang-172-192242.html\">MU n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/barca-vs-tottenham-tran-dau-icc-2018-ngay-hom-nay-372-192222.html\">Barca 2-2 (pen 5-3) Tottenham (KT): L\u1ee9a m\u0103ng non La Masia th\u1eafng b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lenglet-tuyen-bo-san-sang-chien-dau-o-barca-180-192211.html\">Lenglet tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-barcelona-tuyen-bo-se-no-them-bom-tan-180-192202.html\">HLV Barcelona tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 th\u00eam bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/everton-tien-gan-toi-chu-ky-lucas-digne-180-192181.html\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Mina, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u201ch\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca thanh l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1768","checkdouble":"192281"},{"date":"14:48 29/07","title":"HLV Barca l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/hlv-barca-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ousmane Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Ousmane Dembele thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 105 tri\u1ec7u euro ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n sau 19 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf La Liga.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/HLV-Ernesto-Valverde-phat-bieu-ve-Ousmane-Dembele-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ousmane Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Camp Nou \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Barca ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh. Sau khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Antoine Grizmann v\u00e0 Willian, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca mua Malcom th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u euro, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/dembele-muon-chay-tron-khoi-barca-180-191966.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ousmane Dembele mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca</span> \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Hi\u1ec7n Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Valverde tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Dembele</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/HLV-Ernesto-Valverde-phat-bieu-ve-Ousmane-Dembele-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Ernesto Valverde tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Barca v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n\u00a0</span>Dembele</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Barca. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i Dembele d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cDembele \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho Barca v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Dembele n\u1eefa. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Dembele c\u1ea3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ed1t cho m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, t\u00f4i tin Dembele v\u00e0 Malcom s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1767","checkdouble":"192253"},{"date":"15:24 29/07","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wilfried Zaha n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Crystal Palace \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zaha c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Crystal Palace \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Wilfried Zaha l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace. C\u1ef1u sao M.U \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Selhurst Park tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wilfried Zaha n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Wilfried Zaha n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPalace d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn cho Zaha, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i. \u1ede b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Zaha \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Crystal Palace. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, anh mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWilfried Zaha n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Crystal Palace \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram: \u201cH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn mang t\u00ednh b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n b\u1ecf theo d\u00f5i Crystal Palace tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Zaha</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Wilfried Zaha, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea. The Blues nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Eden Hazard ra \u0111i. Pochettino c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/co-doi-bong-chi-40-trieu-bang-mua-hang-thai-mu-172-182476.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham mua Zaha </span>\u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mua Zaha voi gia 40 trieu bang\" title=\"Tottenham mua Zaha v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/20/man-city-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-hang-thai-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Zaha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCrystal Palace t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Zaha \u1edf l\u1ea1i, song n\u1ebfu bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Selhurst Park mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Zaha \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Crystal Palace s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Palace b\u00e1n Zaha v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1766","checkdouble":"192254"},{"date":"14:56 29/07","title":"Valverde n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi t\u00e2n binh Barca ghi b\u00e0n ngay tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/hlv-valverde-noi-ve-man-ra-mat-cua-arthur.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua Grealish. CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Aston Villa c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi sau khi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong b\u00e0i to\u00e1n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham quan t\u00e2m Grealish</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong v\u00e0i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, Jack Grealish lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng l\u1eaft l\u00e9o, c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua, Grealish c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho Aston Villa. Anh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o m\u00ecnh gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111\u00e1 chung k\u1ebft play-off l\u00ean Premier League ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Fulham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua Grealish h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua Grealish h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Tottenham-gap-kho-vu-mua-Grealish-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n Grealish s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Aston Villa l\u1ea1i n\u1ed5i l\u00ean. Trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Man United, Liverpool v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Tottenham.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian qua, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Aston Villa g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp n\u00e0y, Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Birmingham v\u00e0 tin ch\u1eafc s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Grealish\" title=\"Jack Grealish\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/tottenham-gap-kho-vu-mua-grealish.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Aston Villa quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1eddi th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u1ef7 ph\u00fa Nassef Sawaris c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Wes Edens c\u1ee7a M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c mua l\u1ea1i Aston Villa. T\u1ed5ng t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00ean t\u1edbi 40 t\u1ef7 b\u1ea3ng, con s\u1ed1 l\u1edbn th\u1ee9 3 trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. Sawaris v\u00e0 Edens l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u01a1m ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 The Villa thanh to\u00e1n c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3n t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Aston Villa s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00e0 Grealish l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn d\u00e0nh cho Tottenham, \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean U21 Anh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-ra-dieu-kien-mua-alderweireld-cho-mu-172-192150.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 sao Tottenham, M.U ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chot-thoi-diem-tottenham-va-mu-trao-doi-bom-tan-172-191994.html\">Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Tottenham v\u00e0 MU trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-tai-ngo-modric-172-191894.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/harry-kane-noi-gi-khi-tottenham-quyet-dinh-dung-ngoai-ttcn-172-191864.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Tottenham quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i TTCN?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1765","checkdouble":"192255"},{"date":"15:24 29/07","title":"Ander Herrera n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-4 c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/ander-herrera-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-14-cua-mu-truoc-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ander Herrera ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 h\u1ecd thu v\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o trong 90 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ander Herrera ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ander Herrera ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Ander-Herrera-phat-bieu-ve-MU-sau-tran-thua-1-4-truoc-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, M.U \u0111\u1ec3 America c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SJ Earthquakes. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i AC Milan.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-liverpool-tran-dau-icc-2018-dem-nay-372-192208.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U \u0111\u00e3 thua tan n\u00e1t 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool</span>. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 tung ra s\u00e2n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Sanchez, Herrera, Smalling... trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y cho th\u1ea5y M.U t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, Mourinho v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Herrera kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t c\u1ee7a M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ander Herrera ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ander Herrera phat bieu ve MU\" title=\"Ander Herrera ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/ander-herrera-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-14-cua-mu-truoc-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ander Herrera ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3. Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea5y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi 2 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh trong m\u1ed7i hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTrong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi AC Milan v\u00e0 Liverpool, h\u1ecd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1edbi 16 ho\u1eb7c 17 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i 1 nh\u01b0ng b\u00ean ph\u00eda ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 10. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng\u201d.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ed5 \u00edch sau nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 4 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1764","checkdouble":"192256"},{"date":"15:49 29/07","title":"Chelsea chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Higuain","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Higuain. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc AC Milan d\u00f9 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Juventus.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea v\u00e0 Milan \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Higuain</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Juventus, Giuseppe Marotta x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3 Chelsea v\u00e0 AC Milan \u0111\u1ec1u quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Gonzalo Higuain. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fac sau s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Cristiano Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd nghi\u00eam t\u00fac xem x\u00e9t c\u00e1c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb g\u1eedi t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc kh\u00e9o m\u00e0 Bianconeri d\u00e0nh cho Chelsea v\u00e0 Milan trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-Higuain-cua-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nThe Blues chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Mirror c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Chelsea d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Higuain. L\u00fd do n\u1eb1m \u1edf ch\u1ed7 h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 120 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, The Blues c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho Higuain t\u1ea1i b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri. Higuain t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y m\u00f9a 2015/16 t\u1ea1i Napoli. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec9nh cao s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi 36 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Serie A ch\u1ec9 sau 35 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p \u0111\u01b0a anh t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 90 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Milan, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Higuain nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n. Sau nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i chi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Rossoneri gi\u1edd \u0111ang h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a UEFA.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y Chelsea ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Higuain. H\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani. C\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 2 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Sarri khi \u00f4ng c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Empoli.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/drinkwater-muon-roi-chelsea-o-he-2018-172-192252.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c Stamford Bridge</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-olivier-giroud-172-192243.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua Olivier Giroud</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/chelsea-bat-ngo-muon-so-huu-ngoi-sao-cua-arsenal-187-192241.html\">Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dong-y-ban-willian-cho-mu-172-192197.html\">N\u00f3ng: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n \u201ctr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng\u201d Mourinho cho M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1763","checkdouble":"192257"}]}